content.text:
what go code can be used to retrieve and display nutritional information for a list of healthy foods on an html page?
here's an example go code snippet that can be used to retrieve nutritional information for a list of foods and display it on an html page:
package main
import (
"encoding/json"
"fmt"
"io/ioutil"
"net/http"
)
type nutrient struct {
name string `json:"name"`
unit string `json:"unit"`
value float64 `json:"value"`
