```
this pattern starts with the letter "h", followed by zero or more non-digit characters, then the exact word "hello", followed by zero or more non-digit characters, and ends with the letters "abc".
to use this pattern in c++, you can use the `` library. here's an example code that finds all the matching strings in the provided list:
```cpp
